rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0001
rows.name:
The number of refugees from
Superbia just keeps growing.

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0002
rows.name:
I hear Acedia sank near the World
Tree, and so everyone evacuated to
Superbia and Invidia all at once.

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0003
rows.name:
And so, some of the people from Superbia
wanted to evacuate to the safety of Gula,
and came flocking here in great numbers.

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0004
rows.name:
It might not be my place to
say, but Superbia's situation
is much better than Acedia's.

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0005
rows.name:
I could understand if it were people
from Acedia evacuating here, but
most of them are Superbians...

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0006
rows.name:
I wish they would just endure and
live there, but it feels like we're
just being conveniently used.

rows.label: tlk41700321_06_msg0007
rows.name:
Well, we will accept them. It's
not as if everyone will welcome
them unanimously, though.
